PCA on not-standardized data set

biplot(pca_human, choices = 1:2, cex = c(0.4, 0.8))

PCA on standardized data set

human_std <- scale(human)

pca_human <- prcomp(human_std)

biplot(pca_human, choices = 1:2, cex = c(0.4, 0.5))
